snippet.title: This UI component library is mind-blowing
snippet.description:
Let's explore a free open-source UI library that replicates advanced animations found on the landing pages of top-tier startups. Learn how to code advanced components in React and other JavaScript frameworks. 

Aceternity Components https://ui.aceternity.com/components
ShadCN https://ui.shadcn.com/
Parallax Tutorial https://youtu.be/UgIwjLg4ONk
Fireship Next.js Course https://fireship.io/courses/nextjs/

snippet.title: I built an Apple Vision Pro app... visionOS tutorial
snippet.description:
Learn the basics of VisionOS development for the Apple Vision Pro. I build a simple app from scratch using SwiftUI and RealityKit to build an app for Apple's new VR/AR platform. 

Upgrade to PRO https://fireship.io/pro

VisionOS Docs https://developer.apple.com/documentation/visionos
Apple Vision Code Report https://youtu.be/DuqLkG75BE8
